{"tid":750760,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE《Dance The Night Away》舞太難，單是看舞姿就感覺眼花繚亂了啊","createTime":"2018-07-21T08:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T13:05:45.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9d52449d078f3637a5bb44978ec5fcd71152f8a3","tid":750760,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T08:04:16.000Z","msg":"TWICE這次的新歌《Dance The Night Away》也很洗腦耶！ 不僅旋律讓人過耳難忘，舞蹈的難度也相當大，不過成員們可是為此付出了不少辛苦！<br />\n<br />\n不過從現場版裡看得出，這首歌的舞蹈真的強度超大，動作速度和幅度都不是一般的！ 近日TWICE出演《Section TV》時，MC也提到編舞比往常更激烈，惹得成員們忍不住感謝MC，簡直是說出了大家的心裡話XDD<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5163e4a4f0a72880384aa499c395d0c9/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-07-18/107536-635498.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5163e4a4f0a72880384aa499c395d0c9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-07-18%2F107536-635498.jpg&h=6128b0b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n定延還說：「因為我跟不上舞蹈，甚至還從舞蹈老師那邊申請了個人課程。 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e672bc331309349c5d487fd7f1ee8ead/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-07-18/107536-635500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e672bc331309349c5d487fd7f1ee8ead%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-07-18%2F107536-635500.jpg&h=5a804e5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n志效也說：「對減肥的人非常推薦這首歌！ 因為太累，連食欲都會降低。 」<br />\n<br />\n不過當製作組送上美食時大家都吃得很開心，這時成員們又換了一個說法！ MOMO說：「跳這首歌是不能節食的！ 在舞台上暈倒怎麼行！ 」 娜璉也說：「我們不管多辛苦的行程，3年來我們一次也沒有暈倒過。 」好啦都是你們有道理XDD<br />\n<br />\n真的單是看舞姿就感覺眼花繚亂了啊"},{"pid":"9f44d7b7986e6f78884b7e3bdee284e0b6f6c4c9","tid":750760,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T08:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b458e866a144e309f8e01d708dc91c211a3ebc","tid":750760,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" cl